Interface KFFCombinationCreatorProxy

All Superinterfaces:
oracle.jbo.ApplicationModule, oracle.jbo.ComponentObject, oracle.jbo.ExprWrappable, oracle.jbo.GenericHints, KFFCombinationCreator, oracle.jbo.Properties, oracle.jbo.WarningContainer
public interface KFFCombinationCreatorProxy
extends KFFCombinationCreator

A proxy interface for KFFCombinationCreator. When this interface is used to create a key flexfield combination, the method with the context must be called instead of the method inheried from KFFCombinationCreator; however, classes that implement this interface still have to implement the method inheried from KFFCombinationCreator. In general, the implementation can be placed in the method with the context, and the call to the inheried method can simply be delegated:
